        <item>
            <title>Version 2.1.11</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h1 id="v2111">v2.1.11</h1>

<h3 id="features">🚀 Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>open finder or copy paths on path double-click (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/064c9523cad77bbec8bcd3a83264e69306ba23ef">064c952</a>)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>File Compare: show ignored differences count in diff counters (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/b13e34b89ba86f27935e02d3f3da0e76eeaafc62">b13e34b</a>)</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="bug-fixes">🐛 Bug Fixes</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>pass a suggested destination for missing compared files (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/38ce8cbe118990ff1ef3e0a5088554d84b0f58fd">38ce8cb</a>)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>restore “Select Adjacent Sections” menu item (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/c55b4a2added428417fa8c0cf13f165a93e61332">c55b4a2</a>)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>File Compare: navigate to next diff pair when current becomes equal after save (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/608fefdfaec444025207bdd6d16eea1a86ef0234">608fefd</a>)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Folder Compare: keep selection on adjacent row after saved file becomes equal (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/b9edae223b7c633dd7a6b5b5418344995ac26263">b9edae2</a>)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Folder Compare: refresh row when item is no longer orphan after save (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/4099d9c8db8748bb322226d54c79f1c9a891a08a">4099d9c</a>)</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="performance">✨ Performance</h3>

<ul>
  <li>File Compare: avoid repeated treeViewFont() calls by using currentFont (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/f3dfc3dfeed4794feb9b2df9813dd06c3c5f3700">f3dfc3d</a>)</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="documentation">📚 Documentation</h3>

<ul>
  <li>document automatic app updates (<a href="https://github.com/visualdiffer/visualdiffer/commit/19772859f26b4d5983f19a5e82f810c2ad608d83">1977285</a>)</li>
</ul>


                ]]>
